linkhome (0.03) intrepid; urgency=low

  *  Added gdm xdg autostart of linkhome
  *  Reduced useless Qt4 deps for linkappd
  *  Update debian package install instructions
  *  Change linkappd.conf to not auto restart firefox
  *  Fix error in nprocess.cpp init of timer
  *  Added Dbus based application start in the LinkHome controller
  *  New application/<app>/launch urls in LinkHome templates
  *  Added gnome-menu icon for LinkHome
  *  Made a few changes to setup.sh to copy more needed files
  *  Make app restarting more robust
  *  Add wait feature to linkappd.conf to delay the 
          starting of firefox before linkhome is started
  *  Add feature to stop trying to restart an application
          if it restarts more than 5 times in 10 seconds
  * Debug notes cleanup

 -- Tom Bruno <tbruno@neurostechnology.com>  Wed, 25 Mar 2009 00:06:15 -0500

